.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, malaysian, spanish, argentine, nigerian, french, turkish
7 different pets are kept: bird, snake, dog, frog, guinea-pig, mouse, horse
 1. the nigerian is on the left of the indonesian##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is the turkish##1
 4. the spanish is on the left of the french##1
 5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the argentine is the owner of the frog##1
 7. the indonesian is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the horse and the argentine##2
 9. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
10. the malaysian is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | turkish | nigerian | indonesian | malaysian   | argentine | spanish | french |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | mouse     | snake     | dog | frog   | bird   | horse    |

