.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, coffee, soy-milk, mirinda, 7up, cola
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, indonesian, egyptian, spanish, british, thai
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the indonesian##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the spanish##1
 3. the british is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the spanish##1
 5. the brazilian is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the egyptian is between the person drinking coffee and the british##2
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
 8. the egyptian is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is the colombian##1
10. the brazilian is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | coffee    | mirinda  | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate  | cola      | 7up       | almond-milk |
| Nationality   | spanish | egyptian | british | thai | brazilian | indonesian | colombian  |

