.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: gospel, salsa, ambient, electronic, funk, reggae, blues
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, trike, car, airplane, tram, roller
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the airplane is the fan of salsa##1
3. the person driving the boat is between the fan of blues and the fan of gospel##2
4. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the person driving the boat is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
8. the person driving the snowmobile is the fan of electronic##1
9. the fan of funk is the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic      | funk | gospel | ambient | blues      | salsa      | reggae |
| Transport     | snowmobile | tram | roller       | boat | trike | airplane | car |

