.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, analyst, journalist, manager, security-guard, lawyer
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, rugby, basketball, ice-hockey, soccer, sailing, skiing
1. the analyst is on the left of the lawyer##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is the manager##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's sport is soccer and the coach##2
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
8. the security-guard is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | manager | coach | journalist | security-guard | dressmaker | analyst     | lawyer |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey    | skiing    | soccer      | rugby  | golf | sailing |

