 3. the person who's sport is handball is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking tea is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person drinking sprite##2
10. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | juice | almond-milk    | soy-milk | tea   | 7up | mirinda    | sprite |
| Sport      | snowboarding | skateboarding | weightlifting    | handball | swimming    | baseball | sailing  |

