 5. the videographer is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking coffee##2
 7. the security-guard is on the right of the paramedic##1
 8. the bartender is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
10. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking milk##2
11. the videographer is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
