.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: fantasy, documentary, epic, mystery, drama, musical, martial-arts
The people use 7 different means of transport: van, roller, helicopter, car, ship, airplane, subway
1. the person watching fantasy movies is the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the ship##2
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
7. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
8. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
