.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade, iced-tea, sprite, juice, soy-milk
The people have 7 different hobbies: fishing, camping, filmmaking, chess, baking, writing, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is camping##2
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is writing##2
9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | almond-milk       | soy-milk         | sprite         | iced-tea   | lemonade        | juice |
| Hobby      | card-games | filmmaking | fishing | baking | camping | writing | chess  |

