5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's hobby is chess##2
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | card-games | fishing       | drawing    | collecting | video-games | chess     | traveling       |
