.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, animation, scientific, drama, disaster, sports
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: country, blues, electronic, ambient, trance, r&b, jazz
 1. the person watching mystery movies is the fan of jazz##1
