 3. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the fan of country##2
 4. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching drama movies##2
 5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 6. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of country##1
 7. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is the fan of trance##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
10. the fan of ambient is the person watching scientific movies##1

