The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, funk, electronic, dubstep, country, blues, metal
 1. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of country##1
 2. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 3. the person drinking coffee is between the fan of classical and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 4. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 5. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the fan of country##1
 7. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 8. the fan of metal is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |      3      |   4    |    5    |   6   |    7     |
| Beverage      | water   | lemonade | cola | coffee | soy-milk | juice   | milk |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | electronic | classical     | country | metal  | funk | blues     |

