 3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating pomegranate##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person eating grapefruit is the person drinking radishade##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is the person eating broccoli##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking sprite and the person eating grapefruit##2
10. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | almond-milk | mirinda | 7up   | sprite   | hot-chocolate     | radishade  |
