 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person eating cranberry is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person eating peach is the person eating peach##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
10. the person eating peach is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
