 6. the person eating strawberry is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the person eating cucumber is the owner of the snake##1
 9. the person eating eggplant is the owner of the pony##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
12. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1

