6. the manager is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
7. the designer is on the right of the fisherman##1
8. the musician is between the person eating carrot and the manager##2
9. the person eating carrot is on the right of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |         5          |        6        |     7      |
| Food   | eggplant | grapes    | tomato | carrot | papaya              | plum      | broccoli    |
| Job    | police-officer | social-worker | fisherman  | designer   | musician | manager | chef |

 